name: Circles 02
description: Circles subdivided numerous times with 100% opacity and white background. Addition of colours is based off a selection of colours with random hue, saturation, and brightness values with limitations on the hue. In essence, a predetermined colour scheme was selected by choosing a number of colours and assigning them each a random hue. Every circle graphed thereon has a random hue value from these predetermined hues limited by the number of colours. Saturation and brightness is randomly selected for each circle independently.
